#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/middleware.md
msgid "Yii works with HTTP using the abstraction layer built around [PSR-7 HTTP message interfaces](https://www.php-fig.org/psr/psr-7/)  and [PSR-15 request handler/middleware interfaces](https://www.php-fig.org/psr/psr-15/)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/structure/middleware.md
msgid "The application is composed of one or several middleware. Middleware runs between request and response.  When the URL is requested, the request object is passed to the middleware dispatcher that starts executing middleware one after another.  Each middleware, given the request, can:"
